text:
EARN EXTRA MONEY! BE YOUR OWN BOSS! We are seeking a ad date: 10/03/2015 
We are seeking a person to deliver newspapers to homes in Brookings. Route is approximately 2-3 hours a day, only 2 times per week, early mornings. This is an independent contracted delivery route. You must be over 18 with a valid drivers license, proof of insurance and reliable vehicles. Must have ability to work with little supervision and provide prompt, This is an excellent opportunity for extra cash to supplement any income. Receive $100 Sign-on Bonus!
